query:
SELECT e.id, e.name, e.userId, u.name as userName, u.email 
FROM employees e 
LEFT JOIN users u ON e.userId = u.id 
WHERE u.email = 'ghadahassen28@gmail.com' OR e.name LIKE '%غادة حسن%';
